      "text": "Stores (valtio)\n\n- Modal\n\n{\n   modal: Renderable (pegar do Guidee acho) \n}\n\n- Kanban\n\n {\n    id: \"\",\n    title: \"\",\n\n    columns: {\n        [\"columnId\"]: {\n            id: \"\",\n            kanbanId: \"\",\n            title: \"\",\n            tasksId: []\n        }\n    },\n\n    tasks: {\n        [\"taskId\"]: {\n            id: \"\",\n            \n            title: \"\",\n            description: \"\",\n            dueDate: \"\",\n            \n            kanbanId: \"\",\n            columnId: \"\",\n\n            createdAt: \"\",\n            updatedAt: \"\",\n        }\n    },\n\n    $columnsWithTasks: {\n        [\"columnId\"]: {\n            [\"taskId\"]: {\n\n            }\n        }\n    } // computed property\n}\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
